                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman</hi> 124 <hi rend="italic">H</hi> s). I heard a cry of "Police? "ran about twenty yards, and saw the prisoner rise from the ground where Lindsey was lying; he ran right into my arms—I found a florin, a shilling, a sixpence, and 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in copper in his trousers pocket—Lindsey charged him—he said that he knew nothing about it—it was quite light, being under a lamp—the others were bigger than the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">COURT</hi> 
